<taxonomicName box="[813,876,925,950]" class="Insecta" family="Crambidae" genus="Gargela" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="54" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="furca">
<emphasis box="[813,876,925,950]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="54">furca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, corresponding to the forklike juxta in male genitalia.
</paragraph>
